Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,憧～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.64,0:00:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,公交呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有3分钟才到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小稳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.07,0:00:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哟  转校生同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也是穿得这么可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这在东京很流行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.87,0:00:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的爱好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在东京也是属于极少数派的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  差不多请不要再用「转校生」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有「可爱小姐」之类的称呼可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  那么  叫你什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫和
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原村和
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们交朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.81,0:01:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:32.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们成为朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.81,0:01:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,====================================
